ThrowableList

public ThrowableList(Throwable t)
Creates a new ThrowableList. The first element of this ThrowableList's iteration will be the supplied Throwable, followed by its cause, and its cause's cause, and so on.

Parameters:
t - the Throwable to iterate over; may be null
